Program: Outlook
Title: The Right of Self Defence
Link: https://www.bbc.co.uk/programmes/p03kbrpt
Last Broadcast Date: Not available
A look at how different countries deal with pleas of self-defence in murder cases. Also, a look at the emotion of jealousy. An interview with female boxing champion Jane Couch. A guided tour of Khartoum on the White Nile. Finally, plans to turn the lights out for one hour on the beach in Malaga, Spain. Show less